room_title: Escape room "Out of Time" by HD Escape Rooms Greeley in Fort Collins
room_description: You’ve done it! After years of research, your team has discovered the secrets to time travel. The only trouble is, no one believes you. What’s worse, while trying to convince your colleagues, your ravings have branded you as “unstable.” Now your team has been locked away in the Greely Sanitarium, but the secret is out. You must race against the clock to break free and collect your findings before a rival scientist, or worse, can use your discovery to change the fabric of history. The sanctity of the past, present, and future lie in your hands at HD Escape Rooms “Out of Time” escape room adventure!
